commit.message:
Issue #75: Update find_latex() for Python 3.9 (#76)

Python 3.9 now normalizes "latex+latin1" to "latex_latin1":
https://bugs.python.org/issue37751

find_latex() now splits the encoding name on "_" if it contains "_",
or split on "+" otherwise.
Add ,, encoding to lower double quote.
Changelog update.

Fix comment matching. (#73)

This closes issue #72
